        "body": "<p>Starting Android 10 (API level 29), there are restrictions on opening an activity from the background. Check this - <a href=\"https://developer.android.com/guide/components/activities/background-starts\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://developer.android.com/guide/components/activities/background-starts<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>You should try to avoid this or you can check these exceptions - <a href=\"https://developer.android.com/guide/components/activities/background-starts#exceptions\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://developer.android.com/guide/components/activities/background-starts#exceptions<\/a>. If any of the exceptions works for you then you can try doing that.<\/p>\n",
